Demo Data

demo_data.Rd

A completely made up demo data set meant to mimic the structure of the NACC data. While IDs look like valid NACC IDs, these are simply the characters NACC with six random digits. Similarly, birth and visit dates are randomly created, and so are all scores with the only constraint that -4's are believable. (For example, if OTRAILA is -4, so is OTRAILB.)

Usage

demo_data

Format

demo_data

The data set contains the following columns:

NACCID

Subject ID number

NACCAGE

Subject's age at visit

SEX

Subject's sex

EDUC

Years of education

BIRTHYR

Subject's year of birth

BIRTHMO

Subject's month of birth

Form date - year

VISITMO

Form date - month

Form date - day
